deck_excerpt: My Kaliss Kashtira deck post-April banlist.
deck_description:
A Maliss deck with the kashtira engine to add additional extension to make up for Link Decoder being banned. It makes the deck more playable under lancea. While I can play Maliss with fiendsmith, I prefer to have more options in the extra deck space.

I will replace Droll with Mulcharmy Fuwalos in the main deck once I get access to it. Droll will be placed in the side deck.
